title: Get search card based on address, points, or polyline
description: Get search card based on address, points, or polyline

fields.name: Address
fields.description: Address to search for, either by input from Users or from the respond from AddressContract. Can be partial address, or fully formed address. Act as the center point of the Polyline

fields.name: Filter
fields.description: Required when making a request to /address/search. Refer to AddressContract's type_filter param.

fields.name: Latitude
fields.description: Center latitude of the search area Or minimum latitude when maxLatitude is provided

fields.name: Longitude
fields.description: Center longitude of the search area Or minimum longitude when maxLongitude is provided

fields.name: Radius
fields.description: Radius of the polyline when only center latitude and longitude is provided

fields.name: Polylines
fields.description: The boundary which defines which Properties should be included in the search result. Returned by linz/boundary/point in base64 encoded format, so should be decoded before it can be used.

fields.name: Limit
fields.description: Control the number of search result returned at a time

fields.name: Page
fields.description: Controls the page number when querying to /map/cards

fields.name: Sort
fields.description: The 'sort by' object that defines how the search result is sorted on. To be used when querying /map/cards. Examples: Not specified = Featured First order: date, direction: asc = Latest order: price, direction: asc = Highest price order: price, direction: desc = Lowest price

fields.name: Order
fields.type:
Order 
 String (optional) 

Order



 Direction 
 String (optional) 

Direction

fields.name: JustSold
fields.description: An additional filter to only show Properties that are recently sold To be used as just_sold parameter when querying /map/cards.

fields.name: OffMarket
fields.description: An additional filter to include Properties that are not currently for sale. Default to true. To be used as off_market parameter when querying /map/cards.

fields.name: DateMin
fields.description: An additional filter to include Properties with date value at least from this value

fields.name: DateMax
fields.description: An additional filter to include Properties with date value at most from this value

fields.name: ForSale
fields.description: An additional filter to include Properties that are currently for sale. To be used as for_sale parameter when querying /map/cards.

fields.name: ForRent
fields.description: An additional filter to include Properties that not currently for rent. To be used as for_rent parameter when querying /map/cards.

fields.name: MaxLatitude
fields.description: MaxLatitude to be used in conjunction with Latitude to define a search area When MaxLatitude and MaxLongitude is specified, polyline will be generated to cover the area within the two coordinates.

fields.name: MaxLongitude
fields.description: MaxLongitude to be used in conjunction with Longitude to define a search area When MaxLatitude and MaxLongitude is specified, polyline will be generated to cover the area within the two coordinates.

fields.name: RequestPolyline
fields.description: When this variable is set to true, the respond will return the polyline used to make the Search

fields.name: OffMarketMin
fields.description: Min price for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

fields.name: OffMarketMax
fields.description: Max price for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

fields.name: OffMarketBathrooms
fields.description: Min bathrooms for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

fields.name: OffMarketBathroomsMax
fields.description: Max bathrooms for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

fields.name: OffMarketBedrooms
fields.description: Min bedrooms for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

fields.name: OffMarketBedroomsMax
fields.description: Max bedrooms for off market properties. It applies to either JustSold or OffMarket.

returns.description: <SoldSearchResponse> A list of search cards from an area

fields.name: SuburbEstimate
fields.description: Formatted price of the suburb’s estimate; E.g 960K, 1.01M

fields.name: SuburbEstimateDate
fields.description: Last updated date for SuburbEstimate; E.g 2023-11-02T00:00:00Z

fields.name: CapitalGrowth
fields.description: Calculated value that indicates the capital growth of the suburb, in percentage unit. The formula to calculate the value will be the same used in Homes. E.g 5.1%

fields.name: Polylines
fields.description: Specified the polylines that was used when searching.
